"3763-20300103R" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. :The device is presumably identical to the [[Linksys WRT320N v1]].
The router has a single radio (i.e. not simultaneous dual-band). :E2000 serial numbers appear to start with '''CVR0'''.
